# ============================================================================
# X (TWITTER) API CONFIGURATION
# ============================================================================

# Get your API credentials from:
# https://developer.twitter.com/en/portal/dashboard

# ============================================================================
# REQUIRED: API KEYS (CONSUMER KEYS)
# ============================================================================

# API Key (Consumer Key)
X_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
# Can also use: TWITTER_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

# API Secret (Consumer Secret)
X_API_SECRET=your_api_secret_here
# Can also use: TWITTER_API_SECRET=your_api_secret_here

# ============================================================================
# REQUIRED: ACCESS TOKENS (FOR USER CONTEXT)
# ============================================================================

# Access Token (for posting, user operations)
X_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_access_token_here
# Can also use: TWITTER_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_access_token_here

# Access Token Secret
X_ACCESS_SECRET=your_access_secret_here
# Can also use: TWITTER_ACCESS_SECRET=your_access_secret_here

# ============================================================================
# OPTIONAL: BEARER TOKEN (FOR APP-ONLY AUTH)
# ============================================================================

# Bearer Token (for read-only operations without user context)
X_BEARER_TOKEN=your_bearer_token_here
# Can also use: TWITTER_BEARER_TOKEN=your_bearer_token_here

# ============================================================================
# API TIER INFORMATION (DETECTED AUTOMATICALLY)
# ============================================================================
#
# X API has 4 tiers with dramatically different capabilities and costs:
#
# FREE ACCESS ($0/month):
#   • 1,500 tweets read per month
#   • 50 tweets write per month (almost useless!)
#   • No media upload
#   • No search
#   • No streaming
#   • Use case: Testing only
#
# BASIC ACCESS ($100/month):
#   • 10,000 tweets read per month
#   • 3,000 tweets write per month
#   • Post with media (photos, videos, GIFs)
#   • Basic search (50 requests/month)
#   • Like, retweet, reply
#   • Follow/unfollow
#   • Use case: Personal/small business automation
#
# PRO ACCESS ($5,000/month ⚠️):
#   • 1,000,000 tweets read per month
#   • 100,000 tweets write per month
#   • Full search API (300 requests/15min)
#   • Real-time streaming (filtered stream)
#   • Direct messages (read/send)
#   • Analytics and metrics
#   • Poll creation
#   • Lists management
#   • Bookmarks
#   • Use case: Social media platforms, brand monitoring, analytics
#   ⚠️  WARNING: $5,000/month = $60,000/year!
#
# ENTERPRISE ACCESS (Custom pricing, starts ~$42,000/month):
#   • Unlimited rate limits
#   • Full Firehose (all public tweets)
#   • Historical data access (full archive)
#   • Advanced compliance features
#   • Dedicated support
#   • Custom integrations
#   • Use case: Large enterprises, government, research institutions
#
# Current tier (detected automatically):
X_API_TIER=FREE

# ============================================================================
# HOW TO GET CREDENTIALS
# ============================================================================
#
# 1. Go to https://developer.twitter.com
# 2. Sign in with your X (Twitter) account
# 3. Create a new app or select existing app
# 4. Go to "Keys and Tokens" tab
#
# X_API_KEY & X_API_SECRET:
#   • Under "Consumer Keys"
#   • Click "Regenerate" if needed
#   • Copy both API Key and API Secret
#
# X_ACCESS_TOKEN & X_ACCESS_SECRET:
#   • Under "Authentication Tokens"
#   • Click "Generate" if not created
#   • Copy both Access Token and Access Token Secret
#
# X_BEARER_TOKEN:
#   • Under "Bearer Token"
#   • Click "Generate" if not created
#   • Copy Bearer Token
#
# ⚠️  SECURITY WARNING:
#   • Never commit .env to git!
#   • Add .env to .gitignore
#   • Never share your tokens!
#   • Regenerate tokens if compromised
#
# ============================================================================

# ============================================================================
# TIER UPGRADE GUIDANCE
# ============================================================================
#
# FREE → BASIC ($100/month):
#   Worth it if you need practical automation (>50 tweets/month write)
#   Steps:
#     1. Go to https://developer.twitter.com/en/portal/products
#     2. Click "Subscribe to Basic"
#     3. Enter payment information
#     4. Confirm subscription
#
# BASIC → PRO ($5,000/month):
#   ⚠️  EXTREMELY EXPENSIVE! Only upgrade if you have business justification.
#   Consider if you truly need:
#     • Full search API
#     • Real-time streaming
#     • Direct message automation
#     • High-volume operations (1M reads/month)
#   
#   This costs $60,000 per year! Ensure ROI justifies expense.
#   
#   Steps:
#     1. Confirm business need and budget approval
#     2. Go to https://developer.twitter.com/en/portal/products
#     3. Click "Subscribe to Pro"
#     4. Review $5,000/month pricing carefully
#     5. Enter payment information
#     6. Confirm subscription
#
# BASIC/PRO → ENTERPRISE:
#   Contact X sales: https://developer.twitter.com/en/enterprise
#   Custom pricing (starts ~$42,000/month)
#
# ============================================================================

# ============================================================================
# RATE LIMIT TRACKING
# ============================================================================
#
# This skill automatically detects your tier and enforces rate limits.
#
# Run these commands to check your tier and usage:
#   npm run twitter test     # Test connection and show tier
#   npm run twitter detect   # Detailed tier detection
#
# ============================================================================

# ============================================================================
# QUICK START
# ============================================================================
#
# 1. Copy this file to .env:
#    cp .env.example .env
#
# 2. Fill in your API credentials from Developer Portal
#
# 3. Test connection:
#    npm run twitter test
#
# 4. Detect tier:
#    npm run twitter detect
#
# 5. Post a test tweet:
#    npm run tweet "Hello from X API! 🚀"
#
# 6. Search tweets:
#    npm run search "AI" -- --number 10
#
# For detailed setup: npm run twitter setup
#
# ============================================================================

# ============================================================================
# COST REMINDER
# ============================================================================
#
# Free:       $0/month       (almost useless - 50 tweets/month write!)
# Basic:      $100/month     = $1,200/year
# Pro:        $5,000/month   = $60,000/year ⚠️
# Enterprise: $42,000+/month = $500,000+/year ⚠️
#
# Always be aware of costs before upgrading tiers!
#
# ============================================================================
